PrecisEnactment of the CANADIAN COMPUTER RESERVATION SYSTEMS (CRS) REGULATIONS which establish the rules for airline computer reservation systems operated in Canada for the purpose of ensuring that information on airline schedules, fares, rules, seat availability, etc., is provided in a comprehensive, neutral manner.
